video_title: Watch This Epic Video If You're Feeling Lazy
transcript:
i will do my best today what does that
mean well it has a different meaning on
any given day some days you feel like
you can't do much other days you feel
like you can take on the world to do
your best means that on either side of
the motivation spectrum you do what you
can to the best of your ability
sometimes that means accomplishing a
goal other times it means just thinking
about that goal if you know you put in
the effort regardless of how big or
small that is more than enough be proud
of your accomplishment you did your best
today so repeat after me
